title: Can't see my club I own. Any help appreciated.
body: I am unable to see my club I own does anyone know how to fix this?

replies.body: There shouldn't be any issues with clubs right now, so we'd like to take a look at your issue and help individually.  Reach out to us in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we can review this, and be sure to include the club name and tag.  We'll get back to you!
